Desc: Amount of reward player will gain. Example "x 150"

English (United States) [en]: Answer questions within the time limit. Answer quickly to get coins!
French: Réponds aux questions dans le temps limite. Répond rapidement pour obtenir des pièces!
Italian: Answer the question within the time limit. For a quick answer you will get a coin
German: Beantworte die Fragen innerhalb des Zeitlimits. Antworte schnell, um Münzen zu bekommen!
Spanish (Spain) [es]: Answer the question within the time limit. For a quick answer you will get a coin

English (United States) [en]: Press the arrow button with the correct answer.
French: Appuie la touche fléchée qui a la bonne réponse.
Italian: Pick an answer using the arrow buttons with corresponding numbers
German: Drücke die Pfeiltaste mit der richtigen Antwort.
Spanish (Spain) [es]: Pick an answer using the arrow buttons with corresponding numbers

English (United States) [en]: You can receive random boosters instead of coin. Don’t miss them!
French: Vous pouvez recevoir des boosters à la place de pièces. Ne les ratez pas!
Italian: You can receive a random booster instead of a coin. Don’t miss it!
German: Du kannst Booster anstelle von Münzen erhalten. Verpass sie nicht!
Spanish (Spain) [es]: You can receive a random booster instead of a coin. Don’t miss it!

English (United States) [en]: Slows down time by 30% for a while.
French: Ralentit le temps de 30% pour une courte periode.
Italian: Temporary slows down the time gauge by 30%
German: Verlangsamt die Zeit um 30% für eine kurze Zeit.
Spanish (Spain) [es]: Temporary slows down the time gauge by 30%

English (United States) [en]: Correct answers fully recover the time gauge.
French: Les bonne réponses remplit la jauge de temps.
Italian: Correct answer fully recovers time while the booster is in use.
German: Richtige Antworten stellen die Zeitanzeige vollständig wieder her.
Spanish (Spain) [es]: Correct answer fully recovers time while the booster is in use.

English (United States) [en]: correct answer award you 10% more points.
French: Une réponse correcte vous accorde 10% de points supplémentaires.
German: Für jede richtige Antwort bekommst du 10% extra Punkte.
